# Synthetica: Advanced UI/UX Prototype Walkthrough

> [!TIP]
> The automation flow is complete! Synthetica has bridged the final gap between manual config files and a high-end, dynamic graphical experience with automatic Web MetaGraph resolution.

## Phase 4 Highlights (Metadata Resolution & Wow Factor)

### Dynamic Config Injection
- Eliminated `.env.local` restrictions entirely! You can now paste your **OpenAI API Key** securely right into the `localhost:3000/settings` UI page.
- We added a native input field for an **Anti-Detect Browser WebSocket Endpoint** (`ws://127.0.0.1:9222/devtools...`). Paste your string there, hit Save, and the backend engine will automatically bypass the headless browser entirely and plug straight into Kiki Login.

### Automated Target Logo Recognition
- Built a brand new `/api/metadata` NodeJS backend endpoint that rips out the OpenGraph tags and favicons of any URL you type in.
- Inside `/settings`, there is a new **Exact Target Sites** block. Type `https://news.ycombinator.com` into the URL field, and click **Add**.
- **The Wow Factor**: Synthetica will instantly resolve the web domain, fetch its highest resolution logo across the web, and mount it into a sleek, floating UI card with an Avatar image using standard Shadcn primitives! 

